{
  "stem": "18486.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So the Jewish people who were in the house would run from the back door immediately into there, in there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then there was a-- there was an opening with a wall which you could put aside.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You couldn't see that at all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had to try that out with all kinds of lights, and even with a glass pot and the sun shining in it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we knew they could never find that opening if they didn't know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there, they could slide that away, and he could get in the coal bin.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And from the coal bin he could get in the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was not camouflaged.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, outside?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a coal bin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we made a double spot in that coal bin so that up were some coals.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And under that, it was empty.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from there, they went in that tunnel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Besides, I always let them in and closed it off myself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one day, we had-- we had a non-Jewish hider who was sold by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was the director of the Royal Blast Furnaces in Holland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Director.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was not Jewish, but he had to hide because he had-- they had in the blast furnaces some very important stuff.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know what the name was, [INAUDIBLE] or something, which the Germans wanted.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he had hidden it himself, personally, the director, and hidden a letter to the arts commandant from the German commander in Holland.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And had told him, I, Director-- Van Delden was his name-- have hidden that stuff myself.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You'll never get it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If you get me, you'll get it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we hid him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Van and then capital D-E-L-D-E-N.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was director of Royal Blast Furnace.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
